replies.body:
So, they nerfed mana regeneration items (Grail, Morellonomicon, and maybe even Tear?), they nerfed mana masteries (flat mana instead of mana regen), they nerfed mana regen as stat on a lot of champs, and now they're also removing mana potions.

>100 mana tends to benefit certain types of champions over others

Meanwhile resourceless/energy based champions.  {{champion:238}} {{champion:157}}
